    "# Determinan dan Invers Matriks\n",
    "\n",
    "## A. Menghitung Determinan dengan Ekspansi Baris\n",
    "\n",
    "Rumus ekspansi baris ke-i:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\sum_{k=1}^{n} (-1)^{i+k} a_{ik} M_{ik}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "dengan $M_{ij}$ adalah minor dari matriks $A$ dan $M_{ij} = \\det A_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "$A_{ij}$ adalah submatriks dengan menghapus baris $i$ dan kolom $j$ dari matriks $A_{m \\times n}$ dengan $1 \\leq i, j \\leq n$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from fractions import Fraction"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Soal 1 — Determinan Matriks 2×2\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} -7 & -5 \\\\ 1 & 4 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Proses Ekspansi Baris 1:**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\det(A) = (-1)^{1+1} a_{11} M_{11} + (-1)^{1+2} a_{12} M_{12}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$= (+1)(-7)(4) + (-1)(-5)(1)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$= -28 + 5 = -23$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A1 = np.array([[-7, -5],\n",
    "               [ 1,  4]])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ekspansi baris 1 (indeks 0)\n",
    "a11, a12 = A1[0, 0], A1[0, 1]\n",
    "M11 = A1[1, 1]  # minor (hapus baris 1, kolom 1)\n",
    "M12 = A1[1, 0]  # minor (hapus baris 1, kolom 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "det_manual = ((-1)**(1+1)) * a11 * M11 + ((-1)**(1+2)) * a12 * M12\n",
    "det_numpy  = np.linalg.det(A1)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"a11={a11}, M11={M11}  →  (+1)({a11})({M11}) = {(+1)*a11*M11}\")\n",
    "print(f\"a12={a12}, M12={M12}  →  (-1)({a12})({M12}) = {(-1)*a12*M12}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\ndet(A1) manual = {det_manual}\")\n",
    "print(f\"det(A1) numpy  = {round(det_numpy)}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Soal 2 — Determinan Matriks 3×3\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} 0 & 2 & -3 \\\\ 1 & -2 & -1 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Proses Ekspansi Baris 1:**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\det(A) = (-1)^{1+1}(0) M_{11} + (-1)^{1+2}(2) M_{12} + (-1)^{1+3}(-3) M_{13}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Karena $a_{11}=0$, suku pertama = 0.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$M_{12} = \\det\\begin{bmatrix}1 & -1 \\\\ 0 & 1\\end{bmatrix} = (1)(1) - (-1)(0) = 1$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$M_{13} = \\det\\begin{bmatrix}1 & -2 \\\\ 0 & 0\\end{bmatrix} = (1)(0) - (-2)(0) = 0$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\det(A) = 0 + (-1)(2)(1) + (+1)(-3)(0) = -2$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A2 = np.array([[ 0,  2, -3],\n",
    "               [ 1, -2, -1],\n",
    "               [ 0,  0,  1]])\n",
    "\n",
    "def minor(M, i, j):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Menghitung minor M_ij: hapus baris i dan kolom j (0-indexed)\"\"\"\n",
    "    sub = np.delete(np.delete(M, i, axis=0), j, axis=1)\n",
    "    return np.linalg.det(sub)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ekspansi baris 1 (indeks 0)\n",
    "det_manual2 = 0\n",
    "i = 0\n",
    "for k in range(3):\n",
    "    cofactor = ((-1)**(i+k)) * A2[i, k] * minor(A2, i, k)\n",
    "    print(f\"  k={k+1}: (-1)^({i+1}+{k+1}) * {A2[i,k]} * M{i+1}{k+1} = {cofactor:.4f}\")\n",
    "    det_manual2 += cofactor\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\ndet(A2) manual = {round(det_manual2)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"det(A2) numpy  = {round(np.linalg.det(A2))}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Soal 3 — Determinan Matriks 4×4\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & -3 & 1 & 1 \\\\ -3 & 1 & 1 & 1 \\\\ 1 & 1 & -3 & 1 \\\\ 1 & 1 & 1 & -3 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Proses Ekspansi Baris 1:**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\det(A) = \\sum_{k=1}^{4} (-1)^{1+k} a_{1k} M_{1k}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A3 = np.array([[ 1, -3,  1,  1],\n",
    "               [-3,  1,  1,  1],\n",
    "               [ 1,  1, -3,  1],\n",
    "               [ 1,  1,  1, -3]])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ekspansi baris 1 (indeks 0)\n",
    "det_manual3 = 0\n",
    "i = 0\n",
    "for k in range(4):\n",
    "    m = minor(A3, i, k)\n",
    "    cofactor = ((-1)**(i+k)) * A3[i, k] * m\n",
    "    print(f\"  k={k+1}: (-1)^({i+1}+{k+1}) * ({A3[i,k]}) * M{i+1}{k+1} \"\n",
    "          f\"[minor={m:.2f}] = {cofactor:.4f}\")\n",
    "    det_manual3 += cofactor\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\ndet(A3) manual = {round(det_manual3)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"det(A3) numpy  = {round(np.linalg.det(A3))}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## B. Invers Matriks dengan Rumus Adjoin\n",
    "\n",
    "Rumus:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$(\\text{adj}\\, A)_{ij} = (-1)^{i+j} M_{ji}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A^{-1} = \\frac{1}{\\det A} \\, \\text{adj}\\, A$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def adjoin(M):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Menghitung matriks adjoin (transpose dari matriks kofaktor)\"\"\"\n",
    "    n = M.shape[0]\n",
    "    cofactor_matrix = np.zeros((n, n))\n",
    "    for i in range(n):\n",
    "        for j in range(n):\n",
    "            cofactor_matrix[i, j] = ((-1)**(i+j)) * minor(M, i, j)\n",
    "    return cofactor_matrix.T  # adjoin = transpose kofaktor\n",
    "\n",
    "def invers_adjoin(M):\n",
    "    det = np.linalg.det(M)\n",
    "    if abs(det) < 1e-10:\n",
    "        return None, det\n",
    "    adj = adjoin(M)\n",
    "    return adj / det, det"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Soal 4 — Invers Matriks 2×2\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} -7 & -5 \\\\ 1 & 4 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Langkah-langkah:**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. $\\det(A) = (-7)(4) - (-5)(1) = -28 + 5 = -23$\n",
    "\n",
    "2. Kofaktor:\n",
    "   - $C_{11} = (+1)(4) = 4$\n",
    "   - $C_{12} = (-1)(1) = -1$\n",
    "   - $C_{21} = (-1)(-5) = 5$\n",
    "   - $C_{22} = (+1)(-7) = -7$\n",
    "\n",
    "3. $\\text{adj}(A) = \\begin{bmatrix} 4 & 5 \\\\ -1 & -7 \\end{bmatrix}$\n",
    "\n",
    "4. $A^{-1} = \\dfrac{1}{-23} \\begin{bmatrix} 4 & 5 \\\\ -1 & -7 \\end{bmatrix}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A4 = np.array([[-7, -5],\n",
    "               [ 1,  4]], dtype=float)\n",
    "\n",
    "inv4, det4 = invers_adjoin(A4)\n",
    "adj4 = adjoin(A4)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"det(A4) = {round(det4)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\nMatriks Adjoin:\")\n",
    "print(adj4)\n",
    "print(f\"\\nA4^(-1) = (1/{round(det4)}) * adj(A4):\")\n",
    "print(inv4)\n",
    "print(f\"\\nVerifikasi A4 * A4^(-1) (harus I):\")\n",
    "print(np.round(A4 @ inv4, 10))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Soal 5 — Invers Matriks 3×3\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} 0 & 2 & -3 \\\\ 1 & -2 & -1 \\\\ 0 & 0 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Langkah-langkah:**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. $\\det(A) = -2$ (dari Soal 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "2. Hitung semua kofaktor $C_{ij} = (-1)^{i+j} M_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "3. $\\text{adj}(A)$ = transpose matriks kofaktor\n",
    "\n",
    "4. $A^{-1} = \\dfrac{1}{\\det(A)} \\, \\text{adj}(A)$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A5 = np.array([[ 0,  2, -3],\n",
    "               [ 1, -2, -1],\n",
    "               [ 0,  0,  1]], dtype=float)\n",
    "\n",
    "inv5, det5 = invers_adjoin(A5)\n",
    "adj5 = adjoin(A5)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"det(A5) = {round(det5)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\nMatriks Kofaktor (sebelum transpose):\")\n",
    "n = A5.shape[0]\n",
    "cof = np.zeros((n,n))\n",
    "for i in range(n):\n",
    "    for j in range(n):\n",
    "        cof[i,j] = ((-1)**(i+j)) * minor(A5, i, j)\n",
    "print(cof)\n",
    "print(f\"\\nMatriks Adjoin (= transpose kofaktor):\")\n",
    "print(adj5)\n",
    "print(f\"\\nA5^(-1) = (1/{round(det5)}) * adj(A5):\")\n",
    "print(inv5)\n",
    "print(f\"\\nVerifikasi A5 * A5^(-1) (harus I):\")\n",
    "print(np.round(A5 @ inv5, 10))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Soal 6 — Invers Matriks 4×4\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & -3 & 1 & 1 \\\\ -3 & 1 & 1 & 1 \\\\ 1 & 1 & -3 & 1 \\\\ 1 & 1 & 1 & -3 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Langkah-langkah:**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. $\\det(A)$ dihitung dari Soal 3\n",
    "\n",
    "2. Hitung semua 16 kofaktor $C_{ij}$\n",
    "\n",
    "3. $\\text{adj}(A)$ = transpose matriks kofaktor\n",
    "\n",
    "4. $A^{-1} = \\dfrac{1}{\\det(A)} \\, \\text{adj}(A)$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A6 = np.array([[ 1, -3,  1,  1],\n",
    "               [-3,  1,  1,  1],\n",
    "               [ 1,  1, -3,  1],\n",
    "               [ 1,  1,  1, -3]], dtype=float)\n",
    "\n",
    "inv6, det6 = invers_adjoin(A6)\n",
